TO INSTALL

Assuming:
    - you have a jars project at /var/www/myportal
    - working jars binary exists at /var/www/myportal/jars
    - your project requires oranfry/jars-refreshd (composer)

Run once:
$ sudo apt install inotify-tools

Run for each project (myportal, ...):
$ sudo cp /var/www/myportal/vendor/oranfry/jars-refreshd/jars-refresh@.service.example /etc/systemd/system/jars-refresh@myportal.service
$ sudo systemctl daemon-reload
$ sudo systemctl enable jars-refresh
